org.apache.hadoop.hive.ql.plan

Class SparkWork

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hive.ql.plan.AbstractOperatorDesc
      • org.apache.hadoop.hive.ql.plan.SparkWork
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable, OperatorDesc

    public class SparkWork
extends AbstractOperatorDesc
    This class encapsulates all the work objects that can be executed in a single Spark job. Currently it's basically a tree with MapWork at the roots and and ReduceWork at all other nodes.
    See Also:
